Following a photograph by the famous Syrian war photographer Yaser Murtaja, depicting war heroes holding a gun in their jaws, proven through test, hundreds of teenagers in Sarajevo and Tuzla subordinated to their cameras and pretended they’ve eaten it, without realizing how silly they looked. They rushed over the internet and started doing it as well! As soon as the news about this local phenomenon spread, more and more users in Bosnia and the world tried to copy this, and Events even published it! Here are the images of blindly immersed people following one man’s foolish message.

NEW FASHION TREND :

This fashion trend is spreading all over Bosnia and Herzegovina. Everybody seems to wear these sexy and comfortable Adidas tracksuits and shirts in one national uniform.

We can’t just feel proud for out new national fashion, also all of our famous rappers are excited to be on the same level as Beyonce ! Saza Hercegovac is also recovered and interested.

This girl spends around 75 000KM to look like Bobbi Brown, Beyonce or Angelina Jolie.

A little creation made in Tuzla by a 16 year old aspiring designer Branka Ahmic, created an amazing collection with her friend Marija. Unfortunately she quit high school two years ago but her only goal were her outfits.
